products.name: ASC AR-15/M4/M16 Rifle Magazine Stainless Steel .223/5.56 10/rd
products.description:
The ASC AR-15/M4/M16 Stainless Steel magazines are constructed with the highest levels of quality that guarantees durability and longevity! Their magazines are manufactured 100% start to finish in the USA using “.020” gauge 410 Stainless-Steel Alloy that is heat treated for superior strength and lasting endurance. Stainless-Steel construction means they won’t swell in heat or crack in the cold making a more reliable alternative to polymer magazines. This is done all while maintaining that undeniably good look.

  • 410 Series Stainless Steel Body Heat Treated
  • Chrome Silicon Springs
  • Enhanced Anti-tilt Polymer Followers with PTFE
  • 300 Series SS Floor plate with Black Oxide Coating for Corrosion Resistance

With a 30-round capacity it is perfect for various shooting applications including tactical scenarios target practice or hunting. The magazine's sturdy aluminum build ensures longevity and resilience under different shooting conditions. This magazine is compatible with .223 Remington/5.56mm NATO ammunition making it versatile for use with various AR-15 rifles.   • Versatile Compatibility: Suitable for use with a wide range of AR-15 rifles making it a versatile choice for different shooting needs.

products.name: Amend2 AR-15 Polymer Rifle Magazine Black MOD-2 Model .223/5.56 30/rd
products.description:
The Amend2 AR-15 Polymer Magazine MOD-2 Model is a top-tier accessory that brings a new level of precision and reliability to your AR-15 rifle. With a generous 30-round capacity this magazine is designed to meet the needs of both tactical professionals and recreational shooters.

Crafted from a durable black polymer the Amend2 MOD-2 Magazine is both lightweight and robust ensuring it can withstand the rigors of any shooting environment. Its sleek design not only enhances the aesthetic of your AR-15 but also offers comfortable and reliable handling. The polymer material provides resistance to impact protecting your ammunition and ensuring consistent performance.

  • Sturdy Impact resistance polymer with textured grip
  • Anti-tilt super follower
  • Heavy duty non-memory and non-corrosive stainless steel spring
  • Made in the U.S.A.
  • Material able to cerakote

One of the standout features of the Amend2 MOD-2 Magazine is its anti-tilt follower. This innovative design ensures smooth feeding of rounds reducing the likelihood of jams and misfeeds. The follower's engineering guarantees that each round is aligned correctly providing a seamless shooting experience.

The magazine's spring is made from high-quality material that maintains its strength and elasticity over time. This means you can count on the Amend2 MOD-2 Magazine for many years of reliable service. Its 30-round capacity makes it an excellent choice for extended shooting sessions whether you're on the range or in the field.

The Amend2 MOD-2 Magazine is also designed for easy disassembly and maintenance. Cleaning and upkeep are straightforward ensuring that you can keep your magazine in top condition with minimal effort.

The Amend2 AR-15 Polymer Magazine MOD-2 Model is a must-have for any AR-15 owner. Its combination of high capacity durable construction and flawless functionality makes it an excellent choice for anyone looking to upgrade their shooting experience.

products.name: Amend2 AR-15 Mod-C Rifle Magazine Glow in the Dark 5.56x45/.223 Rem 30/rd
products.description:
Featuring a chemical and shock-resistant translucent polycarbonate body the Amend2® AR-15 .223/5.56 30-Round Mod-C Translucent Magazine is the ultimate rifle magazine for tactical operators competitive target shooters and backyard plinkers alike. Designed to withstand heavy use and abuse under any shooting conditions this magazine comes equipped with an aggressive grip texturing for a slip-resistant grip with wet sweaty or gloved hands resulting in faster mag changes and reloads. The proprietary 4-way anti-tilt self-lubricating follower and the non-memory steel spring work together to ensure smooth jam-free operation when it matters most. This 30-round AR-15 magazine also features precision-molded and reinforced polycarbonate feed lips for a tight wobble-free fit while the removable base plate allows for quick disassembly when maintenance and cleaning are required. Made in USA.

  • 4-way anti-tilt follower.
  • Heavy-duty non-memory and non-corrosive stainless steel spring.

The Amend2 Mod-C 30-round magazine is the ultimate rifle magazine for tactical operators competitive target shooters and backyard plinkers alike for the AR-15 chambered in 5.56 NATO (5.56x45mm) and .223 Remington. The "VICE" part of the name signifies its unique custom "Miami Vice" teal translucent finish. It is constructed from a durable impact-resistant polymer with a stainless steel spring and anti-tilt follower. 

  • Capacity: 30 rounds
  • Caliber: 5.56 NATO / .223 Remington
  • Model: Mod-C (Modification C)
  • Color: Translucent teal with a custom "Miami Vice" graphic
  • Material: Impact-resistant polycarbonate
  • Spring: Heavy-duty non-corrosive stainless steel
  • Follower: Anti-tilt
  • Origin: Made in the U.S.A.

products.name: Amend2 Short-Action Magnum AICS Rifle Magazine 6.5 PRC 3/rd
products.description:
Crafted with meticulous precision right here in the USA the 6.5 PRC 3-round magazine is the embodiment of American excellence in engineering quality and rugged design. This magazine is engineered to meet and exceed the demands of even the most discerning shooters and professionals.

Designed with a patented variable thickness wall structure that allows for proper fitment and feeding of the larger 6.5 PRC cartridge.

Constructed with reinforced impact-resistant polymer it can withstand the harshest conditions and keep delivering flawless performance. It is equipped it with a long-life heavy-duty non-corrosive non-memory spring that is built to last shot after shot year after year.

6.5 PRC magazine is fully compatible with SAAMI spec 6.5 PRC cartridges.

FEATURES:

  • Designed and manufactured in the USA with American parts and craftmanship.
  • Ruggedly designed with reinforced impact-resistant polymer.
  • Anti-tilt self-lubricating follower.
  • Long life heavy duty non-corrosive non-memory spring.
  • Heavy-duty impact-resistant paint pen style matrix design for easy identification.
  • Tool-less disassembly for quick ammo dump and cleaning.
  • Limited lifetime warranty.
  • Compatible with SAAMI spec 6.5 PRC

products.name: Area 419 Universal SA Magazine Extension Black for ARC and AICS Magazines 4/rd
products.description:
In Area419's opinion these are the only correctly made mag extensions on the market.  Other magazine extensions on the market are simply rectangular blocks.  If you look at your magazine the bottom is angled so when you attach a competitors extension it is not parallel with the column of cartridges in the magazine.  This probably works fine for +2 rounds but it would not work for much if any more.  Area419 decided to do it right and cut the attachment rail at an angle to the pocket in the mag.  This means that the column of rounds travels straight down into the extension.  This took extra time on the mill and they chose to cut them in one operation on the 4th axis but it was worth it to deliver to you the most advanced product of its kind.  The fluting around the sides make an excellent gripping point for mag changes and also helps to remove some weight.

After starting with the American Rifle Company +4 mag extension Area419 realized that with a little bit of redesign that it could work equally well with AICS an Accurate mags.  The 419 universal mag extensions are designed to work on a variety of magazines from the ARC 10rd mag to AICS 5 or 10rd and Accurate Mag in either standard bolt face or on SAUM/WSM mags. They are NOT COMPATIBLE with AI AW magazines as those have a fixed/welded floorplate.

Easy install great performance and the quality you’ve come to expect from Area 419.

Expected Capacity Increase:
ARC 10-Rounders: +4 or +5 depending on cartridge
AICS & Accurate 10 Rd: +3 or +4 depending on cartridge
AICS & Accurate 5 Rd: +2 or +3 depending on cartridge
Accurate WSM 3 or 7 Rd: +3

NOTE:  **THESE DO NOT WORK WITH MAGPUL OR ANY OTHER POLYMER AI MAGS**

products.name: XS Sight Magazine Tube Detent Swage - Remington 12 gauge
products.description: In the past installing a magazine tube extension on one of the 870/1100/11-87 series of shotguns was as simple as removing the mag cap prying up the magazine spring retainer and swapping out springs before screwing on the extension. With the advent of the detent style magazine spring & mag cap retention system this is no longer possible. Now one has to find a way to remove those detents so the follower can slide past them.

products.name: Advance Warrior Solutions Pistol Triple Mag Pouch Black
products.description: Experienced shooters know that ammo is scarce and precious; have backup ammo ready at the ready and then some. The AWM Pistol Triple Mag Pouch is a low profile lightweight solution to an often burdensome problem. Versatile enough to be used on just about any rifle or pistol AWM has you covered with a wide assortment of magazine pouches that will neatly fit your spare magazines. With a MOLLE attachment you can attach this mag holster to a large variety of existing modular platforms and the AWM material is rugged enough to withstand the most rigorous of environments. These pouches fit most standard and high capacity mags. Compatible with a variety of magazine calibers AWM Pistol Mag Pouches are the bomb-proof choice when you need to quickly access your ammunition.

products.name: Butler Creek Hot Lips Banana Magazine Ruger 10/22 Smoke Polymer 25/rd
products.description:
The Butler Creek Hot Lips Banana Magazine for the Ruger 10/22 rifle is a game-changer for both competitive and recreational shooters. Offering a substantial 25-round capacity this magazine is designed to enhance your shooting experience with its high-capacity design and reliable performance. Made from a durable smoke polymer it ensures longevity and resilience against wear and tear making it an ideal addition to any Ruger 10/22 setup.

Key Features:

  • Extended Capacity: Enjoy more shooting and less reloading with a generous 25-round capacity.
  • Robust Construction: The smoke polymer build offers durability and a sleek look.
  • Smooth Feeding: Designed for reliability ensuring smooth feeding without jams.
  • Compatibility: Perfectly fits Ruger 10/22 rifles enhancing performance and ease of use.
  • Easy Maintenance: Simple to clean and maintain ensuring long-term functionality.

Butler Creek's dedication to quality and performance is evident in the Hot Lips Banana Magazine. Its high-capacity design is not just about offering more rounds; it's about providing a seamless shooting experience with reduced reloading times. Whether you're at the range or in the field this magazine stands up to the demands of varied shooting environments.

The Hot Lips magazine is not only functional but also stylish with its smoke polymer material adding a modern touch to your Ruger 10/22. Its compatibility with the Ruger 10/22 ensures that it integrates seamlessly with your rifle providing a reliable and efficient feeding mechanism that you can count on during every shot.

For Ruger 10/22 owners looking to upgrade their magazine capacity while ensuring reliability and durability the Butler Creek Hot Lips Banana Magazine is an unparalleled choice. Its combination of high capacity robust construction and seamless compatibility makes it a must-have accessory for enhancing your shooting performance.

products.name: CMMG MkW-15 Rifle Magazine .458 SOCOM Lancer 10/rd
products.description:
After extensive testing of magazines on the market for 458 SOCOM the Lancer L5 Advanced Warfighter Magazine was the top choice due to the polymer body and steel feed lips. The CMMG-modified Lancer L5-AWM takes this top of the line magazine and perfects it for the wide range of 458 SOCOM on the market by modifying the way the feed lips hold the 458 SOCOM without machining or weakening the steel feed lips. Laser Engraved 458 SOCOM. 10 round capacity. NOTE: This magazine is a modified 30rd 5.56 magazine and as such can still hold 30rds of 5.56 ammo. The magazine has been modified to function properly with 10rds of .458 SOCOM but will physically hold 11rds if forced. Due to the many state restrictions on magazine capacity we will not ship these magazines to individuals in the following restricted states:

  • Hawaii
  • Maryland
  • Massachusetts
  • New Jersey
  • New York
  • California
  • Connecticut
  • Colorado
  • Washington D.C.
  • Chicago Aurora Oak Park Illinois
  • South Bend Indiana

FEATURES:

  • Hardened steel feed lips
  • Impact resistant polymer body
  • Top of magazine catch is steel
  • Non-tilt follower
  • Constant curve internal geometry
  • Stainless steel spring
  • Aggressive texturing on body for positive grip
  • Slim body design
  • Slide on bottom easy to dissemble
  • Designed Tooled Manufactured and Assembled in the USA

products.name: Chip McCormick Power Mag Plus Colt 1911 Handgun Magazine .45 ACP Stainless Steel 8/rd
products.description:
The Chip McCormick Power Mag Plus represents the pinnacle of magazine engineering for the full-size 1911 handgun. Designed specifically to accommodate .45 ACP cartridges this magazine features a robust stainless steel construction ensuring durability corrosion resistance and a long service life. With an 8-round capacity it meets the needs of both competitive shooters and enthusiasts who demand reliability in their firearms.

Key Features:

  • Alloy Frame Compatibility: The unique POWER+ follower is designed to be safe for use with 1911 handguns that have aluminum alloy frames preventing damage when the slide is released on an empty magazine.
  • Stainless Steel Construction: Crafted from heavy-duty corrosion-resistant stainless steel the magazine body stands up to rigorous use and challenging environments.
  • Innovative Follower Design: The POWER+ follower remains within the magazine tube ensuring smooth feeding without contacting the frame ideal for alloy frame 1911s.
  • Easy Maintenance: Comes with a removable base pad allowing for quick and effortless cleaning.
  • CM Products Guarantee: Backed by CM Products' 100% satisfaction guarantee highlighting their commitment to quality and customer satisfaction.

This magazine is not just about holding rounds; it's about providing a reliable feeding mechanism that enhances the shooting experience. Whether you are at the range in competition or relying on your 1911 for self-defense the Power Mag Plus ensures that every round counts. Its laser-welded tube and high-tensile Rocket Wire spring guarantee consistent performance and a smooth reload every time.

The Chip McCormick Power Mag Plus is more than an accessory; it's an essential upgrade for any 1911 owner looking for enhanced performance reliability and peace of mind making it a standout choice in the world of handgun magazines.

  • Caliber: .45 ACP
  • Capacity: 8 rounds
  • 1911 Size: Full Size
  • Unique POWER MAG PLUS follower is alloy frame safe!
  • Heavy-duty corrosion resistant stainless steel body
  • Laser welded tube
  • Numbered witness holes for visual round count
  • Unique all-steel follower also functions as a spring
  • High tensile Rocket Wire spring
  • Removable base pad for easy cleaning
  • Smooth finish for easy insertion and removal
  • Long lasting function in dirty environments
  • CM Products 100% satisfaction guarantee!

  • High tensile Rocket Wire spring
  • Drilled for base pad (base pad and screws sold separately)
  • Flush fit for minimal bulk and easy concealment
  • Smooth finish for easy insertion and removal
  • Long lasting function in dirty environments

products.name: TangoDown Vickers Tactical Magazine Floor Plates for Glock 5pk Black
products.description:
Few people understand modern combat pistol craft like Larry Vickers. After countless hours behind the pistol he understands what will fall short in a gun fight. The one small flaw that could ruin your day is the OEM magazine base pad. It's undersized and offers nothing should your empty magazine fail to drop free for a number of real world reasons.

The VT Magazine Floor Plates are flared with grooved non-slip scallops for positive finger purchase. Stubborn magazines are easily extracted whether muddy caked with ice or sand. Great for one handed reloads too..just hook magazine floor plate under your belt and extract quickly. Molded dimples allow for easy marking and numbering of magazines.

products.name: TangoDown Vickers Tactical +2 Magazine Extension for Glock 43 VTMFP-006 43
products.description:
When Glock recently released the long-awaited single stack 9mm G43 shooters everywhere rejoiced. Finally the Austrian brand had a truly compact concealable pistol that could be worn comfortably anywhere anytime. The upside is the G43 has all of the features you_d expect from Glock.

The downside is _ it_s almost too small. For shooters with medium to large size hands the pistol grip is just too short forcing a finger or two off the weapon when firing. Not the best form to control a 9 x 19 mm defensive handgun cartridge accurately. The 6 + 1 ammunition capacity wasn_t exactly confidence inspiring either.

The fix just arrived. Vickers Tactical & TangoDown Inc. announced the +2 Magazine extension for the Glock G43.

Injection molded of the same durable material used in the magazine body itself the extended floorplate shape was designed to comfortably accommodate a proper firing grip. With 2 additional rounds on board ammunition capacity is now 8 + 1 in the weapon. Also included is a new longer smooth feeding heat-treated stainless steel spring with 100% last-round slide lock backs that are guaranteed.

The VTMFP-006 43 +2 Magazine Extension consists of Extended Floorplate Floorplate Retainer and Stainless Steel Spring. Kit converts 1 Glock magaizine.

FEATURES:

  • Extended shape allows proper firing grip
  • Longer stainless steel spring guarantees 100% last round lock back.
  • Increases magazine capacity to 8 rounds
  • Available in Black only
  • OA Length: 5.75_
  • Weight: .04 oz
  • Made in USA

products.name: Ed Brown Handgun Magazine .45 ACP 8/rd
products.description: Engineered as a true 8 round magazine this magazine has all the features of the original 7 round magazine that has proven itself over the last century. Features that you know it should have like a steel follower heavy duty spring and super-tough base pad. The magazine tube has been lengthened and the base pad wraps around securely to properly accommodate the 8th round while keeping the original ultra-reliable follower design. The integral base pad easily removes for disassembly and cleaning of the magazine. A special finish process makes this magazine tube and follower very slick while staying dry to repel dirt and burnt powder. This makes it super easy to load and insert in the gun by eliminating any extra friction against the follower. The non-slip oversized base pad allows for a secure grip no matter what the conditions. The 88 blank number templates on the bottom allows you to easily number and track usage of your mags from 0 up to 99 if you desire (think digital numbers on a standard alarm clock). If you want the most reliable highest quality 8 round magazine you can buy look no further!

products.name: Daniel Defense Rifle Magazine 12 Pack 5.56mm 32/rd
products.description:
The DD Magazine is the only one worthy of the Daniel Defense name and is built with the same legendary quality and exacting standards as our world-class firearms. Its 32-round capacity for 5.56mm and 300 Blackout rounds is the most notable enhancement while maintaining the same size as industry-standard 30-round magazines. The DD Magazine bulk pack offers AR-15 magazines that surpass the standard in strength and durability with their lightweight cutting-edge carbon-fiber-reinforced polymer construction. An improved feed-lip design and an enhanced anti-tilt follower provide smooth reliable feeding while an impact-absorbing baseplate design adds to the magazine’s overall durability. The textured body gives the shooter a firm grip on the magazine while reloading in any situation with or without gloves. For reliability durability ease of maintenance and legendary Daniel Defense quality go with the name you can trust.

Each DD Magazine bulk AR-15 12-pack consists of twelve individually packaged magazines.

  • Lightweight carbon-fiber-reinforced polymer construction
  • Surface grip feature for performance-driven control in all situations
  • Improved feed lip design for optimized feeding and reliability
  • Impact absorbing baseplate design for long-lasting durability
  • Enhanced anti-tilt follower for reliable feeding
  • Easy to disassemble for cleaning
  • Snag-free design
  • Patent pending
  • Made in the USA

This magazine is intended for use in compact sized XD-M and  XD-M Elite .45ACP models effectively converting the grip from compact to full size. The included magazine sleeve as noted aligns with the installed backstrap already on the pistol creating a seamless transition from compact to full size and allowing the user extra capacity in a compact platform.  To ensure proper fitment magazine with sleeve #1 needs to be used with backstrap #1.  

Note: Requires removal of magwell for proper fitment on XD-M Elite Compact models.  Current production .45ACP XD-M Elite pistols ship from factory with Backstrap #1 installed.

products.name: Galco Classic Lite 2.0 Shoulder System Holster for S&W J Frame Natural RH
products.description:
Since 1970 Galco has made the most comfortable versatile and most copied shoulder holster systems in the world. If you want a genuine Galco shoulder holster for part-time carry the Classic Lite 2.0 is for you.

The Classic Lite 2.0 gives you all the comfort and versatility of our professional-grade shoulder systems since we use the same connectors to achieve the same great fit and function including our trademarked clover shape Flexalon swivel back plate.

Using Premium Center Cut Steerhide allows us to offer a very reasonably priced alternative shoulder system with a proven track record. And you thought an ill-fitting nylon rig was the only affordable choice!

This system includes holster harness double ammo carrier and a set of harness fasteners. Optional accessories and components may be purchased separately including commonly-used items like tie-downs.

Features:

  • Premium Center Cut Steerhide
  • Horizontal gun carry
  • Vertical double magazine carrier with secure flaps
  • Comfortable 1.5" wide harness straps
  • Swiveling Flexalon backplate
  • Accepts tie-downs/cuff case/accessory attachments
  • Fits chests up to 56"

products.name: Galco Miami Classic Shoulder System for Colt Gov't 1911 Tan RH
products.description:
Galco's Miami Classic is quite possibly the most imitated shoulder holster system in the world. A direct descendant of the original shoulder system first introduced by Galco in 1970 (then the Famous Jackass Leather Company) the Miami Classic has since become the favorite of professionals worldwide.

A key component of this patented shoulder system is its spider harness. All four points of the spider harness pivot independently and are connected by our unique clover shaped Flexalon swivel back plate which is a Galco trademark. This results in a perfect fit and lasting comfort for all sizes and shapes.

This system is constructed of premium saddle leather and includes holster harness ammo carrier and a set of system screws. The Miami Classic is fully modular. Optional accessories and components may be purchased separately.

products.name: Galco Miami Classic II Shoulder System Holster for Colt 1911 5" Tan RH
products.description:
Refined and modernized for the 21st century Galco's Miami Classic II improves on the original Miami Classic.

Carrying a handgun in the same horizontal position as the Miami Classic the Miami Classic II orients its spare ammo carrier in a horizontal position allowing a faster and more natural grasp when reloading.

A key component of this shoulder system is its spider harness. All four points of the spider harness pivot independently and are connected by our unique clover shaped Flexalon™ swivel back plate which is a Galco trademark. This results in a perfect fit and lasting comfort for all sizes and shapes. The Miami Classic II's harness straps are 1 1/2" at their widest point distributing weight while also remaining concealable.

This Miami Classic II is constructed of premium steerhide and includes holster harness ammo carrier and a set of harness fasteners. The Miami Classic II is fully modular. Optional accessories and components may be purchased separately including commonly-used items like tie-downs.

With numbered rear-facing witness holes the orange follower accurately counts loaded rounds or indicates a clear chamber. In addition the polymer baseplate can be removed when needed giving you access to the inner workings of the magazine for any desired cleaning or maintenance.

NOTE: GLOCK MAGAZINES CAN BE VERY DIFFICULT TO LOAD WHEN NEW. OFTEN THE LAST ROUND WILL NOT FIT UNTIL THE MAGAZINE HAS UNDERGONE A BREAK-IN PERIOD. IT IS RECOMMENDED THAT THE MAGAZINE BE LOADED WITH ALL BUT THE LAST ROUND AND LEFT FOR A FEW DAYS TO COMPRESS THE SPRING. CYCLING THE MAGAZINE FROM FULL TO EMPTY MULTIPLE TIMES CAN ASSIST IN THE BREAK-IN PERIOD.

products.name: Glock Factory Original Glock 32 Magazine .357 SIG 13/rd Pkg'd
products.description:
These Glock 32 357 Sig 13/rd magazines come with springs that are notably rigid often making it a challenge to fully load them. To assist in this process a Glock magazine loader typically included in the handgun's case is a useful tool for achieving full or near-full capacity.

When you find it difficult to fit the final round into a 15-round magazine only managing to insert 14 rounds a useful method is to leave the magazine filled with these 14 rounds for a few days. Doing so eases the spring's tension a bit making it more likely for the magazine to eventually hold all 15 rounds. Even so you may still need to use a magazine loader after this initial period. With repeated use as you load and empty the magazine several times it will gradually become easier to load.

The G32 .357 13-Rd Magazine Package offers Glock 32 owners a high-capacity reliable magazine solution. Designed for durability and consistent feeding this magazine enhances the performance of your firearm making it perfect for both tactical situations and everyday carry.

products.name: HS Precision Pro-Series AP300/AP305 Short Action Low Capacity Rifle Magazine .308 Win 4/rd
products.description:
More than simply a convenient way to carry ammunition a quality magazine is an integral part of the function of any precision rifle. H-S Precision magazines whether standard or high capacity provide superior protection for projectiles and flawless feed.

  • .308 Win only

H-S Precision stainless steel conversion kits are designed to convert your Remington 700 BDL hinged floor plate over to a detachable magazine box feeding system. The external dimensions of the floor metal are identical to those of a factory hinged floor plate. Meaning this system will fit any stock with minor to no inletting required. The Pro-Series floor metal is constructed of stainless steel which is teflon coated in a matte black finish. It features two positive lock spring tension levers on the bottom of both sides of the floor metal. These levers create resistance against the polymer coated boot on the bottom of the magazine box to ensure a tight fit and eliminate any rattle whether the box is empty or full. The skeletonized latch located on the front front ot the trigger guard works in conjunction with the robust spring to ensure a positive ejection of the magazine box every time even with gloves on. Each kit comes with installation instructions but for more information of how easy it is to convert your hinged floor plate over to a detachable magazine watch their "Converting to a Detachable Magazine" video.

Designed to fit your AR-15 pattern rifles chambered in .223 Remington and 5.56x45mm. This drum magazine feeds alternately from the left and right drums with the assistance of two follower belts resulting in a fixed center of gravity while firing. The reinforced feed lips and tension arms are made of solid steel. While a loaded aluminum 30 round magazine weighs about 1.5 lbs the rugged KCI USA drum weighs only 2.2 lbs (1 kg) unloaded and 5 lbs (2.27 kg) loaded. A simple loader is included with each magazine making loading fast and easy. This package includes the KCI USA 100 Round Drum Operator’s Manual Carrying Pouch Graphite Lubricant and Loader.

Disclaimer:  Lifetime Warranty VOIDED if customer disassembles magazine! This magazine is not designed to be used with hollow point ammo.

NOT COMPATIBLE WITH SOME AR-15 / M16 / M4 RECEIVERS THAT DO NOT HAVE THE SAME INTERNAL AND EXTERNAL DIMENSION OF A MIL-SPEC LOWER RECEIVER!

Specifications

  • Weight: 2.2lbs
  • Compatibility: AR-15 / M16 / M4
  • Caliber: .223 Remington / 5.56x45mm
  • Capacity: 100 Rounds
  • Body Material: Polymer / Steel
  • Spring Material: Music Wire

products.name: KCI USA AK-47 Rifle Drum Magazine 7.62x39mm 75/rd Black
products.description:
Designed to fit your AK-47 / AKM pattern rifles chambered in 7.62x39mm. The magazine feeds from a central column resulting in a fixed center of gravity while firing. These lightweight 75 round steel drum magazines load from the back so you don’t have to insert rounds under tension. Ready for any contingency they can be stored indefinitely at the full 75 round capacity with no tension on the spring. When ready for use twist the tension key to provide proper spring tension.

Disclaimer:  Lifetime Warranty VOIDED if customer disassembles magazine! This magazine is not designed to be used with hollow point ammo.

Specifications

  • Weight: 2.1lbs
  • Compatibility: AK-47 / AKM
  • Caliber: 7.62x39mm
  • Capacity: 75 Rounds
  • Body Material: Steel
  • Spring Material: Stainless Steel
  • Finish: Cation Electrodeposition Coating

products.name: Maglula Kel-Tec PMR-30 / CMR-30 LULA Loader & Unloader .22WMR Black
products.description:
Maglula LULA loader & unloader for Kel-Tec PMR-30 / CMR-30 .22WMR magazines.

  • Simple to use
  • Eliminates thumb pain and injury
  • Eliminates wear on feed lips
  • Prolongs magazine life
  • Lightweight and fit in pocket
  • Reliable in all weather
  • Durable reinforced polymer

    Note : Due to a thin wall of .22WMR round case minor deformation to the case may form by the rim pressure of a new loaded round (against magazine’s spring force). This can happen during hand-loading and by using magazine loaders. Try using rounds of higher wall thickness and avoid using rounds where dents are substantial. Contact the ammo manufacturer for safety instructions.

products.name: MagLULA UpLULA - Universal Pistol Mag Loader 9mm thru .45 ACP Black
products.description:
The Maglula UpLULA is a military-grade pocket-size universal pistol magazine loader and unloader designed to load and unload virtually all* 9mm Luger up to .45ACP single and double stack magazines of all manufacturers. It also loads most .380ACP single and double-stack mags and 1911’s mags. The UpLULA loader self-adjusts to the magazine and loads it easily painlessly and reliably.

  • Loads all* 9mm Luger .357 Sig 10mm .40 and .45ACP cal. single and double stack magazines. including 1911 mags of all manufacturer and also loads most .380ACP single and double-stack mags.
  • Pocket-size. One size fits all. No inserts spacers or adjustments at all.
  • Easy loading; the rounds just drop in with no thumb pushing or pressing.
  • No more pain ! Load hundreds of rounds painlessly.
  • Protects your fingers and mags.
  • Up to one round per sec. loading rate. 1/3 the time loading several mags with thumb.
  • Fits in hand and pocket weighs only 66 grams (2.3 Ounce).
  • Highly durable.

*The UpLULA does NOT load the following :

  • S&W 7rd 9mm SS for models 908391339133953 & 3954 (Beak too wide does not enter between lips). It will load the S&W Shield magazine
  • Glock G36 6rd .45 SS (Single Stack) (Beak will not retract from the mag.)
  • Glock G37 G38 G39 .45 G.A.P. mags (Beak will not retract from the mag.)
  • Kel Tec PMR-30 mags.
  • Luger P08 (Parabellum) 9mm (round angle in mag too steep)
  • Rounds longer than 33mm like: 9×23 Win .38 Special .357 Magnum .357 Max. .41/.44 Rem. Mag. .44 S&W Special .45 Colt .45 Win Mag. .50AE.
  • May not load the last round in few types of mags.
  • Mags with less than 8.0mm between their lips.

  • Precision Engineering: Mec-Gar's commitment to precision ensures smooth feeding and reliability in every shot.

Mec-Gar renowned for its high-quality firearm magazines brings another masterpiece with this 1911 magazine. This magazine is perfect for both casual shooting and competitive environments where reliability and precision are paramount. The 8-round capacity strikes the perfect balance between firepower and handling. Whether you're practicing at the range or involved in a competitive shoot this magazine ensures your 1911 performs at its peak.

The Mec-Gar 1911 Magazine .45 ACP is an ideal choice for gun enthusiasts who appreciate the blend of American heritage superior craftsmanship and unwavering performance. It's not just an accessory for your 1911; it's a tribute to the freedoms protected by the 2nd Amendment embodied in every round you fire.

Includes a flush and shock absorbing extended floor plate lock.

products.name: Pachmayr Aluminum Speedloader J Frame 5 Shot
products.description: Pachmayr’s new revolver Speedloaders will set the standard for quality and performance. Unlike competitive models which are made of plastic Pachmayr’s Speedloaders are precision CNC machined from solid aluminum. The Speedloader bodies are cut in a polygon shape which produces the smallest possible outside dimensions and allows them to easily fit compact revolvers. The Speedloaders are also equipped with a rattle eliminating o-ring which contacts the cartridge bases and firmly holds the rounds in place. Cartridges are released with a simple twist of the large knurled knob.

products.name: Shield Arms S15 Handgun Magazine Gen3  for Glock 43X & Glock 48 9mm Luger 15/rd
products.description:
The Shield Arms S15 magazine is a patent-pending flush-fitting 15 round magazine for the Glock® 43X and Glock® 48. The S15 is a steel magazine and is the same length as the OEM Glock® 10 round magazine but holds an additional 5 rounds.

Glock® pistols and magazines are known for reliability - the S15 maintains that same Glock® reliability while giving you a 50% increase in magazine capacity in the same overall footprint.

Shield Arms accomplished this increased capacity with their patent-pending magazine geometry allowing the rounds to stagger thereby fitting more in the same amount of space.

Proudly made in the USA.

What changed with the gen 3 magazine? Shield Arms made the following improvements:

New US-based manufacturer

Modular tooling allowing them to make the S15 and S10 magazines simultaneously 

Raised ribs on the back of the magazine allows us to fully match the OEM magazine position in the mag well which should eliminate any tolerance stacking that results from Glock frame variations

New steel new coating new heat treat process - our new steel is slightly thicker tougher and now comes with a new standard black nitrocarburized QPQ finish for a high degree of corrosion resistance

QPQ Nitrocarburizing is a type of surface treatment used to enhance the durability and corrosion resistance of metal parts. The process involves heating the metal in a controlled environment where nitrogen and carbon are introduced to the surface of the metal. This forms a thin layer of a hard compound called "nitrides" which increase the surface hardness of the metal.

During the QPQ Nitrocarburizing process the metal is immersed in a special salt bath and heated to high temperatures. The salt bath contains a mixture of chemicals that release nitrogen and carbon which penetrate the surface of the metal. The process is carefully controlled to ensure that the nitrogen and carbon penetrate to a specific depth creating a uniform layer of nitrides on the metal's surface.

The resulting nitride layer provides many benefits to the metal parts including increased hardness wear resistance and corrosion resistance. This treatment helps to increase the lifespan and durability of metal parts making them more reliable and long-lasting.

Any “scuffing” you see in the surface finish is completely normal and will not affect the durability or corrosion resistance of the steel.

Mag Catch Requirement
It is required to swap out your plastic OEM mag catch with either our standard steel mag catch or our premium steel mag catch. Here's why. If you don't swap your mag catch you may have reliability issues. If you use another manufacturer's mag catch you may have reliability issues. S15 magazines were designed to work with Shield Arms steel mag catches. 

Specifications :

  • 15 round capacity
  • Same length as an OEM Glock 43X/48 magazine
  • Easy to remove impact resistant base pad
  • High lubricity finish options
  • Made in the USA
  • Patent-pending
  • Warranty - Like all Shield Arms products their S15 magazine comes with our 100% lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects.
  • Additionally Shield Arms also offer a Spring for Life Guarantee - wear out your spring get a new one for free for life

products.name: Shield Arms Z8 Handgun Magazine for Glock 43 9mm Luger 8/rd

products.name: Shield Arms Z9 Handgun Magazine for Glock 43 Black 9mm Luger 9/rd
products.description: When Shield Arms released the S15 magazine for the Glock 43X and 48 they changed the concealed carry game. Using steel instead of plastic for the magazine body allowed them to increase the magazine capacity by 5 rounds without changing the dimensions of the magazine. Now they've applied the same concept to the Glock 43. The Z9 magazine is the same length as the OEM 6-round magazine with the pinky extension but the Z9 hold 9 rounds. That's a 50% increase in capacity with a 0% increase in magazine length! A steel magazine body and durable impact resistant base pad means these mags are built to withstand a lot of abuse. A Powercron coating offers superior resistance to corrosion which is great for anyone who carries their pistol in humid environments or near salt water. These magazines work best when paired with a Shield Arms metal magazine release to avoid wearing down the stock plastic release.

products.name: Radian Weapons Anchor and Magwell for Glock 43x/48 Black
products.description:
The Radian ANCHOR + MAGWELL for Glock delivers a rock-solid grip and effortless reloads. 

A tapered screw drives the patented PLANAR-LOK outward causing barbed teeth to bite into the interior sidewalls of the frame locking the ANCHOR into place. This patented design eliminates inward wall flex preventing magazine bind even with large capacity magazines. The MAGWELL dovetails into the ANCHOR at the rear as it’s tooth bites into the front of the frame. The patented ANGLE-LOK detent drives the MAGWELL rearward into position completing the system’s three-way lock up.

products.name: Radian Weapons Backstrap and Magwell for Sig P365-XMacro Grey
products.description:
The Radian P365-XMACRO Backstrap and Magazine Well were designed in tandem to provide users with a rock-solid and enhanced grip on one of the most popular everyday-carry firearms on the market today – The Sig Sauer P365.

The P365-XMACRO Backstrap features aggressive and deep channels which maximize contact surface and enhance overall grip all while remaining forgiving on the hands. The palm swell allows for a repeatable connection resulting in more control of the firearm. This consistency leads to improved performance/accuracy and quicker follow-up shots.

The P365-XMACRO Magazine Well also aids in hand positioning by providing another key point of contact at the bottom of the grip module. The enhanced feed walls ensure reliable tactical and administrative reloading while maintaining a streamlined design. The low-profile characteristics of the system limits printing while concealed carrying as well as reducing snagging occurrences during holstering and unholstering. The Magazine Well maintains compatibility with all OEM P365-XMACRO magazines and base plates/extensions.

The Radian P365-XMACRO Backstrap and Magazine Well install using a precision machined dovetail interface with a patent pending ANGLE-LOK spring-loaded retention stud which lock the two components in place – no screws to come loose or break.

products.description: The Model 079 is a patented holder that features a low cut design for easy magazine grasp. Molded from Safari-laminate it holds magazines tightly in place. The 079 also features an adjustable magazine tensioning device that lets an officer set the exact amount of friction required to remove the two magazines.

products.name: Safariland Model 123 Concealment Magazine Holder Horizontal Plain Black
products.description:
The Model 123 is the best concept in concealed magazine carry to come along in years. Simply wrap the Velcro belt attachment around your belt and a spare clip is ready and accessible. Velcro flap keeps your magazine in the pouch. Wrap the belt flap on top of the closure flap for added security. The ultra-thin membrane Safari-Laminate used in the 123 magazine holder is tough lightweight and durable yet soft. These materials offer an unmatched strength-to-weight ratio. The result is absolute comfort strength and total concealment.

? Single magazine holder? carries magazines in a horizontal position
? Hook-and-loop belt attachment wraps around belt

products.name: Seecamp .32 Magazine Extension Polished Aluminum
products.description:
This extension is fully machined from 6061 Aluminum with a hand polished finish it is designed to fit Seecamp's .32 magazines. It allows the user of the firearm more area to grip the pistol. It does NOT add any additional capacity to the magazine.

Please note that these will only properly fit & function on the “production” Seecamp magazines. A production Seecamp magazine has the Seecamp logo stamped on one side. Larry’s very early hand made magazines will not work with these extensions.

To install simply replace the floor plate of the magazine assembly with the magazine extension (see exploded view)

  • Material: Machined 6061 Aluminum
  • Finish: Hand Polished Aluminum

A fusion of a stainless steel wire spring and a polymer follower guarantees a steady cartridge alignment and feed ensuring you're ready for any scenario. With over 165 years under its belt Smith & Wesson has etched its name as a trusted firearm producer crafting legends like the Model 41 target pistol and the Model 422. 

Boost your firearm's efficiency with the genuine Smith & Wesson Model 422/41/622/2206 Magazine. Made for the .22 LR caliber this 10-round magazine sports a resilient blued finish ensuring longevity and resistance to wear. Crafted to Smith & Wesson's meticulous standards it guarantees a seamless fit and reliable feeding optimizing your shooting experience. Whether you're at the range or in the field trust in the unmatched quality and craftsmanship of S&W.

products.name: Uncle Mike's Pro-Pak Vertical Shoulder Holsters Black - Fits 3-4" Med Autos 3.25-3.75 Lg Auto
products.description:
Pro Pak Series Holsters are made of an extra thin laminate for concealability. Waterproof closed-cell foam padding aids in comfort while providing moisture barrier. Smooth nylon lining further protects gun finish and aids in drawing and reholstering. Simple super-lightweight harnesses are easy to put on and take off with fast hook and loop adjustments. Laminated harness yokes have soft non-abrasive non-slip material on inside; smooth non-stick material on outside that won't hang up on clothing. Non-stretch retention straps and molded thumb/finger breaks are adjusted by hook and loop. Straps are covered with patented Strap Traps to keep straps form stripping away and to prevent chafing; adjustment tool included.

products.name: Ruger Rifle Magazine Black .223 Rem/5.56 NATO 30/rd
products.description:
The Ruger Rifle Magazine designed for .223 Rem/5.56 NATO rounds is an essential accessory for AR-15 rifle owners seeking top-tier performance. This magazine features a 30-round capacity making it an excellent choice for both recreational and tactical shooters who require extended shooting sessions without frequent reloads.

Crafted with precision and attention to detail the Ruger Rifle Magazine stands out for its superior construction. It is made from high-quality materials that ensure both durability and reliability. This robust design means that the magazine can withstand the demands of heavy use in various environments from competitive shooting ranges to harsh outdoor conditions.

One of the key advantages of this magazine is its compatibility with AR-15 rifles. It is designed to fit seamlessly with these popular firearms ensuring smooth and reliable feeding of rounds. The magazine's well-engineered structure allows for easy insertion and removal from the rifle contributing to a hassle-free shooting experience.

The Ruger Rifle Magazine also boasts a user-friendly design. Its surface texture provides a secure grip essential for quick and efficient magazine changes. This feature is particularly beneficial in high-pressure situations where speed and precision are critical.

In addition to its functional benefits the Ruger Rifle Magazine has an aesthetically pleasing appearance. Its sleek black finish not only adds to the visual appeal of the firearm but also provides an extra layer of protection against corrosion and wear.

Overall the Ruger Rifle Magazine is an excellent investment for AR-15 owners. It combines high capacity dependable performance and ease of use making it a preferred choice for a wide range of shooting activities. Whether you are a competitive shooter a tactical professional or a recreational enthusiast this magazine is sure to enhance your shooting experience.

  1. 30-Round High Capacity: Ideal for extended shooting sessions and tactical scenarios.
  2. Compatible with AR-15 Rifles: Designed for seamless integration with popular AR-15 models.
  3. Durable Construction: Built with high-quality materials for long-lasting reliability.
  4. Easy Handling and Operation: Textured surface for secure grip and efficient magazine changes.
  5. Sleek Black Finish: Adds aesthetic appeal and provides corrosion resistance.

30-Round 5.56 NATO/.223 Rem. magazine fits Ruger SR-556 AR-556 and other AR-style firearms. Manufactured in the USA by C Products Defense this improved design features a Stainless Steel two-part body that is robotically welded to control critical-to-function dimensions to ensure proper mag well fit. Each magazine is coated in black Teflon for corrosion resistance and enhanced durability while the stainless steel spring and orange anti-tilt follower are designed specifically for increased feeding reliability. C Products Defense stands by their magazines with a 100% replacement guarantee.

Ruger cannot bill to or ship 30-round magazines to the following states and cities: California Colorado Connecticut Hawaii Maryland Massachusetts New Jersey New York Vermont Washington DC. Illinois Restrictions: Aurora Cicero Skokie Chicago North Chicago Chicago Heights Cook County Buffalo Grove Dolton Hazelcrest Highland Park Homewood Melrose Park Evanston and Oak Park IL. DO NOT ORDER THIS MAGAZINE if you live in these locations. DOES NOT FIT THE RUGER MINI-14 OR THE RUGER MINI THIRTY.

products.name: Glenfield Sled Rifle Magazine for Glenfield Model A Blued .350 Legend .450 Bushmaster 1/rd
products.description: This short-action One Shot Sled is compatible with the Glenfield Model A Rifle. This polymer flush-fit sled allows only a single round to be loaded into the rifle and provides smooth single-round feeding. It is useful to slow down a new shooter or simplify loading during range sessions. The Ruger One-Shot is also ideal for hunting - particularly in states with single-shot hunting regulations such as Illinois. When inserted in the rifle the One-Shot sled fits flush with the stock and does not interfere when carrying a slung rifle or shooting from a bag or backpack. The sled is installed in place of a magazine and is compatible with short-action rifles in several calibers including the 350 Legend 450 Bushmaster 308 Win 243 Win and 6.5mm Creedmoor. This package includes the following components: (1) sled; (1) magazine well; (2) action screws and (1) 3/16'' Allen wrench. This Genuine Glenfield Factory Accessory is made in the USA.

products.name: Wilson Combat Glue-On Base Pad
products.description:
This glue-on base pad increases your stock magazines' length by .360" to provide positive seating without getting too long for practical use.

  • Compatible with all welded base 1911 mil-spec magazines 
  • Applied with a thin film of quality contact cement to the bottom surface

  1. Roughen and degrease all contact surfaces of base pad prior to gluing
  2. Apply a thin film of quality contact cement to both surfaces
  3. Let dry them firmly press the base pad onto the magazine

products.name: Carlson's Universal Shotgun Plug - 2/ct
products.description: Carlson's universal shotgun plug kit allows you to easily decrease the shell capacity from 4 rounds in the magazine tube down to 2 rounds on most shotguns. The plug can be used without cutting but can easily be trimmed to length for other popular guns. Trimming the universal plug to length is best accomplished with a hand held set of pruning shears PVC pipe shears or a hacksaw. Always start with the full plug and cut 1/4? to 1/2? off at a time until only 2 rounds fit in the magazine tube (For fitting purposes use the maximum size shell the shotgun is rated for).

The Sig Sauer P938 9mm extended 7-round magazine is a must-have accessory for P938 owners looking to increase capacity while maintaining a sleek profile. This factory OEM magazine ensures a perfect fit reliable feeding and optimal performance.

Features of the Sig P938 7-Round Magazine

  • Factory OEM quality for guaranteed reliability
  • Extended 7-round capacity for extra firepower
  • Ergonomic design with improved grip and handling
  • Constructed from durable high-quality materials
  • Perfect for concealed carry and tactical applications

Compatibility and Performance

Designed specifically for the Sig Sauer P938 9mm pistol this extended magazine enhances both shooting comfort and capacity. The extended baseplate provides better grip control making it ideal for self-defense and everyday carry.

products.name: Mission First Tactical 10/30 AR15 Rifle Magazine 5.56x45mm .223 Rem .300 AAC 10/rd Bagged
products.description:
The Mission First Tactical 10 round 5.56 NATO polymer magazine engineered as an enhancement of the standard STANAG design. 10 round maximum capacity due to internal limiter. The bottom of the magazine is PERMANENTLY sealed and cannot be readily restored. Gray follower buttons indicates 20 round block. MFT stipple texture low profile front ribs and flared floor plate aid in extraction and handling. The floor plate provides drop protection has a paint pen dot matrix area for easy identification marking and is compatible with tight double and triple magazine pouches. One fully functional drain hole ensures full and proper draining. Long-life stainless steel spring and four-way anti-tilt follower ensure reliable feeding. Oversized mag catch notch in the rear of the magazine provides enhanced reliability of the bolt catch operation.

products.name: Mission First Tactical Belly Band Holster 26? to52? Black Ambi
products.description:
Designed to go wherever you go! The MFT Belly Band Holster is great for walking jogging hiking biking and around town... no belt needed! Comfortable all-day carry is achieved with 3D Spacer Mesh Fabric - Special channels allow for more efficient airflow increasing comfort (in comparison with elastic bands). An Open-Air Weave Construction design provides holes for air/moisture to pass through naturally hindering bacterial growth. Maximum breathability keeps you cool and dry! Soft Medical Grade Hook & Loop construction ensure no chaffing. A self-laminated fastening end is cut/trimmed with scissors for a custom fit. No need for melting binding or stitching to prevent it from fraying.

A Hard Laminate Trigger Shield protects the firearm's trigger from unwanted intrusion. The Belly Band has two Elastic pockets for spare magazine knives flashlights and pepper spray. Two Secure YKK Zippered Storage Pockets are great for credentials cash keys and can double as a phone holder. 

Ambidextrous compatible with a wide variety of firearms. 

Fits waist sizes from 26” to 52”

CARE INSTRUCTIONS: HAND OR MACHINE WASHABLE GENTLE CYCLE LAY FLAT TO DRY.

Fitting Instruction: Place on body snuggly. Locate pinch and cut to remove excess material.  Trim self-laminated fastening end with scissors. No need for melting binding or stitching to prevent it from fraying.

products.name: Mission First Tactical Ultralite Belly Band Holster Black Ambi
products.description:
Designed to go wherever you go! The MFT Ultralite Belly Band Holster is great for walking jogging hiking biking and around town... no belt needed! Comfortable all-day carry is achieved with 3D Spacer Mesh Fabric - Special channels allow for more efficient airflow increasing comfort (in comparison with elastic bands). An Open-Air Weave Construction design provides holes for air/moisture to pass through naturally hindering bacterial growth. Maximum breathability keeps you cool and dry! Ambidextrous compatible with a wide variety of firearms.

products.name: Mission First Tactical AR-15 M-16 M4 M249 SAW FN MINIMI & More Rifle Magazine Black 5.56mm/223 Rem/.300 AAC 30/rd
products.description:
The MFT Standard Capacity Polymer Magazine is a 30 round 5.56 NATO magazine engineered as an enhancement of the standard STANAG design. The MFT stipple texture low profile front ribs and flared floor plate aid in extraction and handling. The floor plate provides drop protection has a paint pen dot matrix area for easy identification marking and is compatible with tight double and triple magazine pouches. Two fully functional drain holes ensure full and proper draining. Simple toolless disassembly with double floor plate safety release tabs allows user to safely release spring tension during disassembly and quick ammo dumps. Long-life stainless steel spring and four-way anti-tilt follower ensure reliable feeding. Oversized mag catch notch in the rear of the magazine provides enhanced reliability of the bolt catch operation. Quality and consistency are ensured by using a specially developed Military Grade reinforced super tough polyamide And as always our products are MADE IN THE USA with a LIFETIME WARRANTY.

products.name: Browning X-Bolt Rotary Rifle Magazine Smoked Bronze .300 PRC 3/rd
products.description:
The X-Bolt rotary magazine is among the lightest most reliable and durable on the market. These magazines are so innovative they have been granted three separate patents. The sturdy polymer construction is designed to endure the punishment that will break lookalikes from competitors. Always keep an extra magazine (or two) in your pocket to facilitate a quick reload when it counts.

Features:

  • Detachable rotary magazine constructed from a durable lightweight polymer
  • Feeds cartridges directly in line with the bolt instead of offset as with traditional leaf-spring magazines for a straight path right into the chamber
  • Ergonomic magazine-mounted release
  • Magnum caliber holds three cartridges
  • Standard caliber holds four cartridges

products.name: Century Arms US Palm AK30 Banana Special Edition Rifle Magazine Banana Yellow 7.62x39 Soviet AK-47 30/rd
products.description:
Century Arms is proud to be a part of bringing the US Palm name and products back to the marketplace. The US Palm designed magazine is instantly recognizable and always dependable and is billed as the most advanced AK-47 30/rd magazine ever. The sealed one piece design is built to endure with a unique blend of polymer. A low friction self cleaning polymer follower keeps performing and the stainless steel latch cage ensures a positive connection between magazine and AK. The waffle and tread pattern helps to distinguish the US Palm from other magazines on the market and this solid magazine will provide you years of enjoyment in any conditions.

products.name: ProMag AR-15 Magazine .223 Blued Steel 30/rd
products.description:
The ProMag AR-15 .223 30-Round Blue Steel Magazine is an exceptional addition to any AR-15 rifle offering both high capacity and outstanding reliability. This magazine stands out for its durable construction designed to withstand the rigors of tactical and recreational use. Its robust steel body treated for heat resistance and finished with a sleek blue oxide ensures long-lasting performance under various conditions.

One of the key features of this ProMag magazine is its 30-round capacity allowing for extended shooting sessions without frequent reloads making it ideal for tactical scenarios target practice or competitive shooting. The magazine's interior boasts a chrome silicon wire spring ensuring consistent feeding and reliability. This spring is designed to maintain tension and function flawlessly over time even with regular use.

The ProMag AR-15 .223 magazine also features a follower that's carefully designed to prevent tilting contributing to its exceptional feeding reliability. This attention to detail in design means that every round is smoothly fed into the chamber reducing the likelihood of jams or misfeeds which is crucial in high-stakes situations.

In addition the magazine’s design allows for easy handling and operation. Its size and shape are optimized for quick and effortless magazine changes while its textured surface provides a secure grip even in wet or slippery conditions. The magazine is also designed to drop free from the firearm when released facilitating quick reloads.

The ProMag AR-15 .223 30-Round Blue Steel Magazine is not only functional but also aesthetically pleasing. Its classic blue steel finish adds a professional and tactical look to any AR-15 setup. It is an ideal choice for shooters who value both aesthetics and performance in their equipment.

  1. Heat-Treated Steel Construction: Ensures durability and resistance to wear.
  2. 30-Round High Capacity: Ideal for extended shooting sessions.
  3. Chrome Silicon Wire Spring: Provides reliable feeding and long-lasting performance.
  4. Anti-Tilt Follower Design: Ensures smooth and consistent ammunition feeding.
  5. Sleek Blue Oxide Finish: Adds a tactical and professional look to the firearm.
  6. MADE IN THE USA

products.name: ProMag Handgun Drum Magazine For Glock 17/19 Black Polymer 9mm Luger 50/rd
products.description:
Sleek yet resilient the ProMag Handgun Drum Magazine designed specifically for Glock 17/19 showcases its robust design marrying functionality with durability. Crafted meticulously for 9mm Luger cartridges this 50-round drum increases your ammunition capacity and maintains an ergonomic design. Its structure ensures it doesn't overpower the pistol's silhouette making it conducive for a stable prone shooting position and efficient storage solutions.

With its cutting-edge technology the Glock 19 drum mag incorporates a straightforward loading mechanism designed to reduce tension from its intrinsic spring system. This 9mm Glock drum further enhances user experience with its transparent back panel enabling shooters to gauge their ammo status swiftly. To assist in cleanliness and longevity it's effortlessly disassembled and a notable feature is its unique bolt-securing system. So if you want to elevate your Glock 17 or Glock 19 with drum capacity this 50-round Glock mag is your ultimate companion ensuring reliability shot after shot.

products.name: ProMag Ruger Mini-14 Magazine .223 Blued Steel 10/rd
products.description:
The ProMag Ruger Mini-14 Magazine designed for .223 caliber ammunition is an essential upgrade for owners of the Ruger Mini-14 rifle. This 10-round magazine is crafted from blue steel providing exceptional durability and reliability. It is perfect for various shooting activities including tactical scenarios and hunting.

ProMag known for its commitment to quality and performance has engineered this magazine to meet the rigorous demands of shooting enthusiasts. The magazine's blue steel construction ensures it can withstand regular use and harsh conditions making it a durable choice for outdoor shooting experiences. Its robust design not only contributes to its longevity but also provides a sleek professional appearance.

The magazine's 10-round capacity is ideal for shooters who require a balance between sufficient ammunition storage and a compact design. This capacity makes it suitable for extended shooting sessions without the need for frequent reloading. Additionally its compatibility with .223 caliber ammunition makes it a versatile choice for various rifle models particularly the popular Ruger Mini-14.

One of the standout features of the ProMag Ruger Mini-14 Magazine is its ease of use. The design allows for smooth and efficient loading and unloading of rounds enhancing the overall shooting experience. The magazine fits seamlessly into the Mini-14 rifle ensuring a secure and snug fit which is crucial for accurate shooting.

Moreover the magazine is equipped with a high-quality spring mechanism that maintains consistent tension ensuring reliable feeding of rounds into the rifle. This feature is vital for maintaining accuracy especially in situations where precision is paramount.

In summary the ProMag Ruger Mini-14 10-round magazine is an excellent choice for Mini-14 rifle owners. Its durable construction optimal capacity and ease of use make it a top choice for shooters who value quality and performance. Whether used for sport hunting or tactical purposes this magazine delivers exceptional reliability and precision.

  1. Durable Blue Steel Construction: Ensures long-lasting performance in various conditions.
  2. 10-Round Capacity: Ideal for extended shooting sessions without frequent reloading.
  3. .223 Caliber Compatibility: Perfect for Ruger Mini-14 and similar rifle models.
  4. Smooth Loading and Unloading: Enhances the shooting experience with efficient operation.
  5. Reliable Feeding Mechanism: High-quality spring ensures consistent round feeding.

Constructed with meticulous attention to detail this magazine is built from heat-treated steel with a black oxide finish ensuring durability and resistance against corrosion.

Designed and made in the USA ProMag emphasizes quality and reliability in every product. The magazine body's robust construction is complemented by an injection molded magazine follower which smoothly guides the 9mm rounds reducing the chances of jams and misfeeds. The magazine spring made from heat-treated chrome silicone wire provides consistent feeding pressure ensuring reliability across numerous firing cycles.

  • Precision Engineered for S&W: Specifically designed for the S&W 908/3913/3914/3953 series for a flawless fit.
  • Durable Construction: Heat-treated steel body with black oxide finish for longevity and corrosion resistance.
  • Reliable Feeding: Features an injection molded follower and a spring formed from chrome silicone wire for consistent performance.
  • USA-Made Quality: Proudly manufactured in the USA ensuring top-notch craftsmanship and materials.
  • Capacity and Compatibility: 8-round capacity in a single stack design optimized for personal defense and competitive use.

This magazine is not only a testament to ProMag's commitment to craftsmanship but also a crucial accessory for S&W pistol owners looking to enhance their shooting experience. Whether for competitive shooting law enforcement purposes or personal defense this ProMag magazine offers the precision and dependability shooters require. Its compatibility with multiple S&W models makes it a versatile choice for a broad range of users.

products.name: Magpul PMAG D-50 Handgun Magazine for Glock 9mm Luger 50/rd
products.description:
Lightweight but incredibly strong othe Magpul PMAG D-50 GL9 is a highly reliable 9x19mm Parabellum 50-round drum magazine optimized for double-stack 9mm GLOCK handguns.

The Magpul D-50 GL9 – GLOCK boasts many of the proven features of its 5.56 and 7.62 predecessors the PMAG D-60 AR/M4 and PMAG D-50 LR/SR GEN M3 while providing the user with a similar magazine capacity increase. Providing 50-round capacity the unique drum configuration keeps the height of the magazine manageable allowing for easier storage. For easy loading it includes a ratcheting loading lever that removes tension from the internal spring.

To keep track of your available firepower Magpul included a rounds-remaining rear window a high-visibility follower and a capacity indication roller.

Easily disassembled for cleaning and featuring an innovative bolt hold-open feature the D-50 GL9 reliably locks the bolt back on empty when used with firearms designed to lock back on GLOCK pattern magazine followers.

It is recommended that you install a new OEM magazine release on Gen 1-3 GLOCK handguns to support the extra weight of the magazine. Gen 4 GLOCK handguns will require an aftermarket metal magazine release. Installation of a new recoil spring assembly to ensure reliable feeding is strongly recommended. Individual variations between firearms may result in an extra power recoil spring being required.

Use of this D-50 GL9 in pistol caliber carbines (PCC) is not recommended because the increased length of the feed tower will be partially unsupported in most pistol caliber magazine wells. This unsupported condition may cause premature wear on the feed tower magazine catch and (in firearms which deviate from factory magazine well specifications) may result in improper round presentation and failures to feed.

Made in the USA.

products.name: Magpul PMAG 20 AR 300 B Gen M3 Rifle Magazine 300 AAC BLK 20/rd
products.description:
The PMAG 20 AR 300 B GEN M3 is a purpose-built magazine for rifles chambered in .300 Blackout (300 BLK). Similar in every way to our PMAG 30 AR 300 B the PMAG 20 is more compact for increased maneuverability and creates a more concealable package for use in small format firearms.

Since its inception 300 BLK shooters have had to use a magazine designed for another cartridge limiting that round’s ultimate performance and compatibility. One of the key features of 300 BLK in the past has been its compatibility with 5.56x45mm magazines. However even with moderate success with that particular magazine it is a compromise to do so with reliability and safety both being at risk.

In addition to the performance gained by a dedicated mag the PMAG 20 AR 300 B also offers a safer way to feed your 300 BLK rifle. When using 5.56x45mm mags the potential to chamber and fire a 300 BLK round in a 5.56x45mm rifle with catastrophic results requires diligent ammunition management by the shooter. The PMAG 20 AR 300 B’s distinct ribbed design and smoother upper-half texture provides the shooter a distinct visual and tactile difference from any other PMAG to mitigate dangerous cross-loading issues.

Along with optimized 300 BLK performance the PMAG 20 incorporates all of our GEN M3 features including our next-generation impact and crush resistant polymer aggressive front and rear texture an easily removable slim floor plate a paint pen dot matrix for marking and identification and a dust/impact cover.

Made in the USA.

products.name: Magpul PMAG 10/30 AR/M4 Gen M3 Rifle Magazine 5.56x45 NATO 10/rd
products.description:
The PMAG 10/30 AR/M4 GEN M3 is a 10-round polymer magazine for AR15/M4 compatible weapons chambered in 5.56x45 NATO/.223 Remington. It was designed for users who reside in areas with magazine capacity restrictions but desire a standard 30-round magazine form.

Built in-line with our other PMAGS the PMAG 10/30 provides the same next-gen impact and crush resistance constant curve geometry and long-life stainless-steel spring to ensure smooth feeding. We’ve added a proprietary lock plate that reduces the maximum capacity to 10 rounds and it’s permanently secured by an aluminum rivet. A lock plate tab that’s clearly marked for capacity is also included. With the standard 30-round magazine form the PMAG 10/30 maintains mag pouch compatibility while complying with local restrictions.

The PMAG 10/30 includes other features found throughout the GEN M3 line. Its redesigned bolt catch notch in the rear of the magazine provides increased bolt catch clearance while an over-travel stop on the spine helps ensure the magazine will not over-insert on compatible weapons. Low profile ribs and new aggressive front and rear texture give positive control of the PMAG 10/30 in all environments and a paint pen dot matrix located at the bottom panel of the body allows for easy marking for identification.

***Not designed or intended to be modified in any way.***

Made in the USA.

products.name: Magpul AMAG 17 SG9 Handgun Magazine for Sig P320/M17 9mm Luger 17/rd
products.description:
When polymer won't work Magpul’s AMAGs will. The same reliability and consistency you expect out of our PMAGs now available in alloy magazines.

The AMAG 17 SG9 is a 17-round 9mm handgun magazine for the SIG P320 family of pistols featuring a heat-treated stainless-steel alloy body with polymer sub-components. Magpul AMAGs come with many of our proven features including a high-visibility controlled-tilt follower stainless-steel spring flared floorplate that’s easily removable for cleaning and routine maintenance paint-pen dot matrix for magazine marking and capacity-indicator windows which begin at five (5) rounds and continue along the spine of the magazine in one-round increments.

Made in the USA.

products.name: Magpul PMAG LR/SR Gen M3 for SR25/M110 Rifle Magazine Black 7.62x51mm/.308 Win 20/rd
products.description:
The PMAG 20 LR/SR GEN M3 Window is a lightweight cost effective highly reliable 20-round magazine for SR25/M110 pattern rifles chambered in 7.62x51 NATO (.308 Winchester). Constructed from next-generation impact and crush-resistant polymer the new magazine features durable dual-side transparent windows which allow for a quick count of the approximate number of rounds remaining in the magazine via a high visibility indicator coil on the spring and numerical markers on the magazine body. This proprietary capability known as the MagLevel system provides a fast round-count estimation without affecting the durability or reliability of the magazine. Like Magpul's other PMAGs the 20 LR/SR GEN M3 Window magazine features a stainless-steel corrosion-resistant spring and an anti-tilt self-lubricating follower. The magazine’s lines follow a constant-curve internal geometry for continuous reliable feeding. The low-profile ribs and aggressive front and rear texturing help give shooters a positive grip for magazine changes in all environments. A paint pen dot matrix at the bottom panel of the body allows easy marking by the end user for identification purposes.

Magpul's standard features include a flared floorplate that aids extraction and handling of the magazine; this flared floorplate also improves drop protection and is slim enough to ensure better compatibility with tight double magazine pouches. The magazine is also simple to disassemble and makes for easy cleaning and maintenance when necessary.

Designed specifically for SAAMI-spec ammunition the PMAG 20 LR/SR GEN M3 Window is less than half the weight of standard issue steel magazines and maintains a service life round count approximately equal to the rifle barrel itself. Accessories designed for the 7.62X51 NATO line of PMAGs are also compatible with the PMAG 20 Window.

Made in the USA.

The magazine’s lines follow a constant-curve internal geometry for continuous reliable feeding. The low-profile ribs and aggressive front and rear texturing help give shooters a positive grip for magazine changes in all environments. A paint pen dot matrix at the bottom panel of the body allows easy marking by the end user for identification purposes.

Magpul's standard features include a flared floorplate that aids extraction and handling of the magazine; this flared floorplate also improves drop protection and is slim enough to ensure better compatibility with tight double magazine pouches. The magazine is also simple to disassemble and makes for easy cleaning and maintenance when necessary.

Designed specifically for SAAMI-spec ammunition the PMAG 20 LR/SR GEN M3 Window is less than half the weight of standard issue steel magazines and maintains a service life round count approximately equal to the rifle barrel itself. Accessories designed for the 7.62X51 NATO line of PMAGs are also compatible with the PMAG 20 Window.

Made in the USA.

products.name: Magpul TMAG AR/M4 Gen M3 Rifle Magazine Translucent 5.56 NATO/.223 Rem 20/rd
products.description:
The TMAG 20 AR/M4 GEN M3 is a highly reliable translucent 20-round magazine for STANAG-compatible weapons chambered in 5.56x45 NATO/.223 Remington. Molded from a durable translucent material with an olive drab hue it provides shooters the ability to visibly verify various ammunition types and the current round count. Featuring ribbed front and rear straps for improved purchase during magazine changes the sides are left smooth to enhance visibility.

Like the rest of the GEN M3 family of magazines the TMAG incorporates similar internal geometry which translates into unmatched reliability when firing. The four-way anti-tilt follower is paired with a durable stainless-steel spring for corrosion resistance. A paint-pen dot matrix allows for custom markings to be applied by the shooter and the TMAG’s low-profile floor plate also allows for compatibility with the full line of PMAG AR/M4 GEN M3 floor-plate accessories.

The TMAG is optimized for Colt-spec AR15/M4 platforms but modified internal and external geometry also permits operation with a range of other weapons such as the HK 416/MR556A1/M27 IAR FN SCAR MK 16/16S and others.

Made in the USA.

products.name: Magpul PMAG 25 ICAR Gen 3 Rifle Magazine Black 6mm ARC 25/rd
products.description:
6mm ARC (6x38mm) provides shooters with a light recoiling accurate and ballistically excellent cartridge option. Our PMAG 25 ICAR GEN M3 Window magazine was designed specifically for the cartridge offering a durable reliable lightweight 25-round 6mm ARC polymer magazine for the Surefire ICAR carbine and other firearms with lower receivers based off the LWRCI Six8 mag well.*

The magazine features a long-life stainless-steel spring four-way anti-tilt follower and constant curve internal geometry for reliable feeling under various environmental conditions. In addition a redesigned bolt catch notch in the rear of the magazine provides increased bolt catch clearance while an over-travel stop on the front spine helps ensure the magazine will not over-insert on compatible weapons. Low-profile ribs and a new aggressive front and rear texture give positive control in all environments and the bottom panel of the body includes a paint pen dot matrix to allow easy marking for identification.

The new easily disassembled flared floorplate aids extraction and handling of the magazine while providing improved drop protection but is slightly slimmer for better compatibility with magazine pouches while allowing for simple disassembly for cleaning purposes. Durable dual-side transparent windows promote easy determination of remaining round count in the magazine when combined with a high visibility indicator coil on the spring and numerical markers on the magazine body. Like other windowed PMAGs the MagLevel system provides positive verification without affecting the durability or reliability of the magazine.

Made in the USA.

products.name: Magpul PMAG 30 AR/M4 Gen M3 5.56x45mm NATO Rifle Magazine Black Polymer 30/rd
products.description:
The Magpul PMAG 30 AR/M4 Gen M3 is an exceptional magazine for 5.56x45mm NATO caliber rifles bringing unparalleled performance and reliability to AR-15 and M4 platforms. This 30-round polymer magazine stands out in the market for its advanced engineering and user-centric design. It features a next-generation impact and crush-resistant polymer construction ensuring durability and longevity even in the most challenging environments.

The PMAG 30 AR/M4 Gen M3 is equipped with a constant-curve internal geometry coupled with an over-travel insertion stop on the spine which guarantees smooth feeding and reliability. The unique design facilitates effortless insertion and removal from the firearm even under stressful conditions. One of the key attributes of this magazine is its anti-tilt self-lubricating follower which ensures consistent feeding of rounds without jamming a critical aspect for both tactical operations and recreational shooting.

Moreover the PMAG 30 AR/M4 Gen M3 features a pop-off impact/dust cover that prevents debris intrusion and protects the rounds during storage and transit. This cover also mitigates potential damage to the feed lips ensuring the magazine's longevity. The magazine’s body is ribbed providing a firm grip for easy handling especially in adverse weather conditions or while wearing gloves.

The Magpul PMAG 30 AR/M4 Gen M3 is not just about functionality; it also boasts a sleek modern aesthetic that complements any AR-15 or M4 rifle. It's an essential accessory for both professional shooters and enthusiasts who demand the best in terms of performance reliability and style.

  1. Impact-Resistant Polymer Construction: Ensures durability and long-term performance.
  2. 30-Round Capacity: Ideal for extended shooting sessions and tactical use.
  3. Anti-Tilt Self-Lubricating Follower: Guarantees smooth and reliable feeding.
  4. Pop-Off Impact/Dust Cover: Protects rounds and feed lips from debris and damage.
  5. Sleek Modern Design: Enhances the aesthetic of any AR-15 or M4 rifle.

The Magpul PMAG D-60 drum magazine is a testament to innovation and reliability. The PMAG D-60 is a durable lightweight highly reliable 60-round 5.56x45 NATO/.223 Remington polymer drum magazine for AR15/M4 compatible weapons. Expanding upon Magpul's legacy this 5.56 drum offers greater capacity than traditional PMAGs. With the PMAG D-60 shooters are equipped with 60 rounds of ammunition essentially matching the round count of two standard capacity 30-round magazines but without the urgency of a pivotal reload.


The unique drum configuration a hallmark of Magpul drums like the PMAG D-60 maintains a manageable height allowing for prone firing and streamlined storage. products.name: Magpul MPMAG800BLK PMAG 30 AR 300 B Gen M3 Rifle Magazine Black .300 Blackout 30/rd
products.description:
The PMAG 30 AR 300 B GEN M3 is a purpose-designed magazine for rifles chambered in 300 Blackout. Since its inception 300 Blackout shooters have had to use a magazine designed for another cartridge limiting its ultimate performance and compatibility. One of the nice features of 300 Blackout is the compatibility with 5.56x45mm parts but with the magazine it is a compromise to do so. Due to the wide variety of projectile weights and profiles potentially decreasing overall reliability a dedicated 300 Blackout magazine was a logical step for the PMAG line.

In addition to the performance gained by a dedicated mag the PMAG 30 AR 300 B also offers a safer way to feed your 300 Blackout rifle. When using 5.56x45mm mags the potential to chamber and fire a 300 Blackout round in a 5.56x45mm rifle with catastrophic results requires diligent ammunition management by the shooter. The PMAG 30 AR 300 B’s distinct rib design and smoother upper-half texture provides the shooter a distinct visual and tactile difference from any other PMAG to mitigate dangerous cross-loading issues.

Whether for competition use or otherwise the PMAG 10 GL9 is the highest quality restricted capacity magazine option available.

products.name: Magpul MAG993BLK PMAG-50 Gen M3 Magazine Black 7.62x51mm LR/SR 50/rd
products.description:
The Magpul PMAG D-50 is a rugged lightweight 50-round polymer drum magazine designed for 7.62x51 NATO/.308 Winchester ammunition for SR25/M110 pattern rifles. It’s capable of using longer-than-SAAMI-spec match ammunition up to 2.830” OAL such as M118LR. Engineered to the same exacting standards as the famous Magpul PMAG and PMAG D-60 drum magazines the D-50 continues the PMAG tradition of high-capacity performance and dependability. --> *Optimized for use only with 7.62x51 NATO/.308 Winchester cartridges. Use with other calibers such as .260 Remington or 6.5 Creedmoor is not recommended. Made in the USA.

  • GEN M3 technology which includes next-generation impact and crush-resistant polymer construction and the ability to seat fully loaded on a closed bolt. Robust stainless-steel internals withstand corrosion and long-term storage while loaded with no loss of function spring fatigue or reliability concerns. A slip-on semi-rigid dust cover prevents grit and debris intrusion during storage and transport.
  • A ratcheting loading lever removes spring tension making the D-50 easily loadable by hand. An anti-glare translucent window on the rear of the drum makes for quick positive visual indication of remaining ammunition. Additionally the D-50 can be disassembled quickly with a simple flat blade screwdriver or similar tool and it comes with a dot matrix pattern that allows for easy marking and identification
  • At approximately 1.7 lbs empty and 4.5 lbs loaded the Magpul D-50 is one of the lightest 50-round 7.62x51/.308 drums available and it's priced well below the current competition. The D-50’s unique drum configuration gives it roughly the same overall height profile as a standard 25-round PMAG making storage easy and shooting from various positions--including prone--no different than with smaller capacity magazines.
  • *NOTE: Compatible with older model Bushmaster .308 ORC Remington R-25 and DPMS LR308 rifles but not optimized for bolt lock functionality with newer models based on the DPMS GII design. NOT compatible with Armalite AR-10B Springfield Armory M1A Rock River Arms LAR8 FN SCAR 17S PTR-91 HK417 or any other rifles that utilize M14 FN FAL or HK 91/G3 patterned magazines.
  • Weight: 1.7 lbs.
  • Width: 4.64”
  • Length: 4.35”
  • Height: 8.34”
